ign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just announced by Bush (09/12/01 10am CST)</span><hr size=1> So far, no ordinance has been taken off the table yet.  All options for retaliation have been kept open.  Even the thought of nuclear attack.  Of course I doubt that would be the case, but you never know.  Bombing takes too long &amp; so would using ground forces.  That would also put more lives of our Americans on the line.  We don't need that.  We should nukem back to the stone age &amp; I hope something of that magnitute or near that is suggested.  Also, I don't think it would be wise for Nato to join in on our retaliation.  We should do it our selves to show that you cannot keep the U.S. down. <p><center><b><i><Font Color="0000CC">Ogkrum Slimfatty - 56 Myrmidon<BR>Saavak Spiritwind - 60 Oracle<P></i></Font><Font Color="009966">"Respect mah AUTHORITAH!"<BR>BazaarCop(tm) of Erollisi Marr<BR</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uzariel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zariel</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www." BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 124<br> <font color=#E9D756>(9/12/01 10:09:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=86.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just announced by Bush (09/12/01 10am CST)</span><hr size=1> What happends -- just suppose for a minute -- the country we attack somehow has a nuclear weapon too?  Renegade scientists, a gift from China, I don't care.  Should they nuke us, too?  Because believe me, if we sent a nuclear force against them, they'd be coming at us with only a few minutes difference.  Or suppose some other country with nuclear weapons comes out on their side?  I don't want to live in post-apocalyptic world.<br>
